<h1 id="the-bare-faced-method">The Bare Faced Method</h1>
<p>Take a good amount of cleanser and cleanse your face for a minute. Wash off with normal water and wait for an hour.</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Do not use any products for an hour.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>There are basically three conditions your face might be in after waiting for an hour.</p>

<h1 id="signs-of-oily-skin">Signs of Oily Skin</h1>
<p>Your skin feels moisturized and sticky without applying any products.</p>

<h1 id="signs-of-dry-skin">Signs of <a href="https://www.sheenycare.com/dry-skin-causes-and-treatment/" target="_blank">Dry Skin</a></h1>
